        <updateDate>2021-02-05T21:48:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>The Resetting the Impact Act (TRIA) of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires certain data collection and recommendations relating to a Medicare post-acute care prospective payment system to incorporate the effects of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) on providers and patients.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
